-- Nakheel Says Creditor Committee Supports $10.5 Billion Restructuring Plan
-- Maher Chmaytelli
-- 2010-07-14T12:20:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/nakheel-says-creditor-committee-supports-10-5-billion-restructuring-plan.html

          
          
              Nakheel PJSC said the coordination
committee of its creditor banks “unanimously supported” its
restructuring proposal, according to an e-mailed statement
today.  
 “Creditor banks will have the opportunity to review the
information provided before responding to the proposal,” it
said. “The company expects to complete the restructuring over
the coming months.”  
